        <a title="Canary" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Canary" href="/user/show/71177188-canary">Canary</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2853846675" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17153898518204923941">I love this trilogy so much. It’s so magical, filled with war, romance and family. I cried more times then I can count, but totally worth it. <br/>While reading this series, I listened to My Indigo’s self titled album on loop and it really set the mood. Now whenever I hear any of those songs, I’m transported back to Akiva and Karou’s love story. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


