  <span id="freeText17810323566810211970" style="display:none">Hi! I write fantasy books. My latest is STRANGE THE DREAMER, about a young librarian, a mythic lost city, and the half-human children of murdered gods. Check it out :-) Before that I wrote the DAUGHTER OF SMOKE &amp; BONE trilogy, which has been translated into 32 languages. It's about a blue-haired art student raised by monsters, a broken angel, and a war that has raged for 1000 years in another world. I also wrote LIPS TOUCH: THREE TIMES, which was a National Book Award finalist, and the DREAMDARK books. As well as various short stories and novellas. <br /><br />Thanks for reading!! <br /><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.lainitaylor.com">www.lainitaylor.com</a><br /><br />@lainitaylor</span>
